column10: The cakes of soap. Flagrantly mislabelled, I only realised that they weren't actual cakes until after the first few bites, but I never knew soap could be so delicious. Thank you for accidentally introducing me to my new favourite snack. On the go, between meals, or after an evening at the pub, a cake of soap is a low-calorie treat that takes "clean eating" to the next level!
